snippet.title: Reset (No Commentary Playthrough)
snippet.description:
Game by Robin Burkinshaw
Music is 'Rest to Reset' by Trash80

Released November 29, 2008 for Windows
Made with Game Maker

Play the game (archived): https://web.archive.org/web/20090126234141/http://www.roburky.co.uk/?p=13
Alternate download: https://archive.org/details/reset-1.13
More information: https://www.mobygames.com/game/225731/reset/
Review of the game by Action Button: https://www.actionbutton.net/?p=601

0:00 Press UP to launch
0:40 Use LEFT and RIGHT to evade
3:35 Press R to Reset
